data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The picture shows a man practicing flying using hydraulic pressure in a rocky area. He is wearing a blue T-shirt on the top and a pair of black shorts at the bottom. He is also wearing a pair of black gloves. The flying device is attached under his feet. The device shoots the water flow downwards to provide a force for the man to fly upwards. The background shows that the man is practicing in a dodgy area with no one but only cliffs and trees.
